What do you mean "It's poorly designed."?
Do you know how much time had to be put into the game to make the physics work and the graphics nearly accurate? Just the simple fact that they could make a 3D game that involves surgery is mind boggling as it is. Then add different effects of all of the tools and you have an amazing game. But yes, the beginning was a little difficult for me. Just keep trying.
